==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stunning
<hw>Stun"ning</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Overpowering consciousness; overpowering the senses; especially,
overpowering the sense of hearing; confounding with noise.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Striking or overpowering with astonishment,
especially on account of excellence; <as>as, <ex>stunning</ex>
poetry</as>.</def> <mark>[Slang]</mark> <au>C. Kingsley.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Stun"ning*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<mark>[Slang]</mark></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stunsail</ent>⟦br⟧
